  "title": "feat(types): rename RenderOptions -> RendererOptions",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\nThis PR rename the type `RenderOptions` used at the renderer level for `RendererOptions`. Widgets   have already types called `InitOptions` & `RenderOptions`. Those types are currently non-exported but it might happen to we have to export them at some point. Anyway it's better to avoid confusion with two types with the same name with almost the same domain.",
